      • getInstance

        public static Car getInstance(java.lang.String carType,
                              RegistrationNumber regisNum)
        Returns a car of the specified type with the specified registration number.
        参数:
        carType - the type of car to return
        regisNum - the registration number
        返回:
        a car of the specified type. An existing car is returned if regisNum is already known. Otherwise a new car with the given number is returned.
        抛出:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if carType is null
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if carType is an invalid carType
